<paragraph id="CC1E36CBFFEBFFA8FF152C83FC41F992" blockId="2.[136,1452,1430,2033]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEBFFA8FF152C83FF58FA63" bold="true" box="[136,241,1430,1456]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">Notes:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="0BA14D48FFEBFFA8FF6D2C83FE76FA63" authorityName="De Candolle" authorityYear="1828" baseAuthorityName="Bonpl." box="[240,479,1430,1456]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Comolia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="berberifolia">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEBFFA8FF6D2C83FE76FA63" box="[240,479,1430,1456]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">Comolia berberifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is the type species of the genus (
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEBFFA8FCC12C83FB99FA63" author="De Candolle, A. P." box="[860,1072,1430,1456]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" refId="ref8849" refString="De Candolle, A. P. (1828) Melastomaceae. In: De Candolle, A. P. (Ed.) Prodromus systematis naturalis regni vegetabilis, sive enumeratio contracta ordinum, generum, specierumque plantarum huc usque cognitarum, juxta methodi naturalis normas digesta. Vol. 3. Sumptibus Sociorum Treuttel et Wurtz, Parisiis [Paris], pp. 99 - 202. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 286" type="book" year="1828">De Candolle 1828</bibRefCitation>
). On the 
<typeStatus id="131A8869FFEBFFA8FB062C83FAABFA63" box="[1179,1282,1430,1456]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">lectotype</typeStatus>
label there are inscriptions “ 
<taxonomicName id="0BA14D48FFEBFFA8FEBD2CAFFDBBFA07" box="[288,530,1466,1492]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Rhexia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="berberidifolia">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEBFFA8FEBD2CAFFDBBFA07" box="[288,530,1466,1492]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">Rhexia berberidifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
” and “ 
<taxonomicName id="0BA14D48FFEBFFA8FDF92CAFFCC0FA07" box="[612,873,1466,1492]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Comolia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="berberidifolia">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEBFFA8FDF92CAFFCC0FA07" box="[612,873,1466,1492]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">Comolia berberidifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
” (
<figureCitation id="549A2A4EFFEBFFA8FC182CAFFC57FA07" box="[901,1022,1466,1492]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="3.[136,229,1866,1888]" captionTargetBox="[242,1345,190,1842]" captionTargetId="figure-18@3.[242,1345,190,1842]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 2. Photographs of the original materials of Comolia berberifolia (Bonpl.) DC. A. Lectotype at P (P00482343). B–D. Details of isolectotype at BR (BR0000008930712). B. Isolectotype with original draft description in the background and the fragment of the type. C. Detail of sketch of the original illustration. D. Fragment of the type. E. Draft description prepared by Cogniaux with the isolectotype at BR. Sources: ©Muséum National d’Histoire Naturelle, Paris, P00482343. Available in: http://coldb.mnhn.fr/catalognumber/mnhn/ p/p00482343. ©National Botanic Garden of Belgium, Meise Botanic Garden, Meise, BR0000008930712. Available in: http://www. botanicalcollections.be/specimen/BR0000008930712." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5423977" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5423977/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">Figure 2A</figureCitation>
), but in the publications of 
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEBFFA8FAA72CAFFECAFA2B" author="Humboldt, F. W. H. A. &amp; Bonpland, A. J. A." pageId="2" pageNumber="249" pagination="105 - 120" refId="ref9434" refString="Humboldt, F. W. H. A. &amp; Bonpland, A. J. A. (1820) Voyage de Humboldt et Bonpland. Monographie des Melastomacees. Rhexies. Libreria Graeco-Latino-Germanica, Paris, pp. 105 - 120. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 16027" type="book chapter" year="1820">Humboldt &amp; Bonpland (1820)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEBFFA8FE072CCAFDD1FA2B" author="De Candolle, A. P." box="[410,632,1502,1529]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" refId="ref8849" refString="De Candolle, A. P. (1828) Melastomaceae. In: De Candolle, A. P. (Ed.) Prodromus systematis naturalis regni vegetabilis, sive enumeratio contracta ordinum, generum, specierumque plantarum huc usque cognitarum, juxta methodi naturalis normas digesta. Vol. 3. Sumptibus Sociorum Treuttel et Wurtz, Parisiis [Paris], pp. 99 - 202. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 286" type="book" year="1828">De Candolle (1828)</bibRefCitation>
the epithet adopted was “ 
<taxonomicName id="0BA14D48FFEBFFA8FC062CCBFB88FA2B" authorityName="De Candolle" authorityYear="1828" baseAuthorityName="Bonpl." box="[923,1057,1502,1528]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Comolia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="berberifolia">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEBFFA8FC062CCBFB88FA2B" box="[923,1057,1502,1528]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">berberifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”. As indicated in the protologue of 
<taxonomicName id="0BA14D48FFEBFFA8FF152F16FE99F9CF" authorityName="De Candolle" authorityYear="1828" baseAuthorityName="Bonpl." box="[136,304,1538,1565]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Comolia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="berberifolia">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEBFFA8FF152F16FE99F9CF" box="[136,304,1538,1565]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">C. berberifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, the original material was deposited at 
<collectionCode id="AAB0AE0EFFEBFFA8FD692F16FCAAF9CE" box="[756,771,1539,1565]" country="France" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15763" name="Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris (MNHN) - Vascular Plants" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" type="Herbarium">P</collectionCode>
(
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEBFFA8FC8E2F17FC41F9CF" author="De Candolle, A. P." box="[787,1000,1538,1564]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" refId="ref8849" refString="De Candolle, A. P. (1828) Melastomaceae. In: De Candolle, A. P. (Ed.) Prodromus systematis naturalis regni vegetabilis, sive enumeratio contracta ordinum, generum, specierumque plantarum huc usque cognitarum, juxta methodi naturalis normas digesta. Vol. 3. Sumptibus Sociorum Treuttel et Wurtz, Parisiis [Paris], pp. 99 - 202. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 286" type="book" year="1828">De Candolle 1828</bibRefCitation>
). It should be noted that the collections deposited at 
<collectionCode id="AAB0AE0EFFEBFFA8FE8B2F32FE8CF992" box="[278,293,1575,1601]" country="France" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15763" name="Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris (MNHN) - Vascular Plants" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" type="Herbarium">P</collectionCode>
were examined by 
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEBFFA8FE622F33FCE5F993" author="Humboldt, F. W. H. A. &amp; Bonpland, A. J. A." box="[511,844,1574,1600]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" pagination="137 - 158" refId="ref9493" refString="Humboldt, F. W. H. A. &amp; Bonpland, A. J. A. (1823) Voyage de Humboldt et Bonpland. Monographie des Melastomacees. Rhexies. Libreria Graeco-Latino-Germanica, Paris, pp. I - II + pp. 137 - 158. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 16027" type="book chapter" year="1823">Humboldt &amp; Bonpland (1823</bibRefCitation>
, see Preface).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CC1E36CBFFEBFFA8FF202F5FFCF4F927" blockId="2.[136,1452,1430,2033]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">
<materialsCitation id="7CC93C96FFEBFFA8FF202F5FFCF0F927" collectionCode="R" collectorName="While &amp; Alexandre Rodrigues Ferreira &amp; Wurdack &amp; Ferreira's &amp; Bonpland &amp; De Candolle &amp; Alexandre" country="Brazil" county="Amazonas" location="Ferreira" municipality="Barcelos" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" specimenCount="1">
<collectorName id="6154531DFFEBFFA8FF202F5FFEA8F9B7" box="[189,257,1610,1636]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">While</collectorName>
studying the collections of 
<collectorName id="6154531DFFEBFFA8FDA32F5FFC39F9B7" box="[574,912,1610,1636]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">Alexandre Rodrigues Ferreira</collectorName>
(1756–1815), 
<collectorName id="6154531DFFEBFFA8FBA52F5FFB34F9B7" box="[1080,1181,1610,1636]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">Wurdack</collectorName>
(1971) highlighted that 
<collectorName id="6154531DFFEBFFA8FF152F7BFF5AF95B" box="[136,243,1646,1672]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">Ferreira’s</collectorName>
collections were examined by 
<collectorName id="6154531DFFEBFFA8FDC02F7BFD63F95B" box="[605,714,1646,1672]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">Bonpland</collectorName>
and 
<collectorName id="6154531DFFEBFFA8FC9B2F7AFC3FF95B" box="[774,918,1646,1673]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">De Candolle</collectorName>
and also attributed the original material of 
<taxonomicName id="0BA14D48FFEBFFA8FA0F2F7AFEA7F97F" authorityName="De Candolle" authorityYear="1828" baseAuthorityName="Bonpl." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Comolia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="berberifolia">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEBFFA8FA0F2F7AFEA7F97F" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">C. berberifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to this collector. 
<collectorName id="6154531DFFEBFFA8FE512F87FDE8F97F" box="[460,577,1682,1708]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">Alexandre</collectorName>
<collectionCode id="AAB0AE0EFFEBFFA8FDDA2F86FDF4F97E" box="[583,605,1683,1709]" country="Chile" name="Departamento de Geologia, Universidad de Chile" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">R</collectionCode>
. 
<location id="C97E6010FFEBFFA8FDFA2F87FD69F97F" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:440887DDFFEBFFA8FF152DF7FB13F823:C97E6010FFEBFFA8FDFA2F87FD69F97F" box="[615,704,1682,1708]" country="Brazil" county="Amazonas" municipality="Barcelos" name="Ferreira" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">Ferreira</location>
carried out numerous scientific activities in the region surrounding 
<collectingMunicipality id="2C7AACB1FFEBFFA8FF152FA3FF43F903" box="[136,234,1718,1744]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">Barcelos</collectingMunicipality>
municipality, 
<collectingCounty id="257F4E47FFEBFFA8FE112FA3FDABF903" box="[396,514,1718,1744]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">Amazonas</collectingCounty>
state, 
<collectingCountry id="B4B6765BFFEBFFA8FDD32FA3FD3CF903" box="[590,661,1718,1744]" name="Brazil" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">Brazil</collectingCountry>
, at the end of the 18 
<superScript id="3BD49B83FFEBFFA8FC1C2FA3FC27F917" attach="left" box="[897,910,1718,1732]" fontSize="6" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">th</superScript>
century (
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEBFFA8FC672FA3FB25F902" author="Goeldi, E. A." box="[1018,1164,1718,1745]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" refId="ref9037" refString="Goeldi, E. A. (1895) Ensaio sobre o Dr. Alexandre R. Ferreira: Mormente em relacao as suas viagens na Amazonia e sua importancia como naturalista. Typ. e Papelaria de Alfredo Silva &amp; C. ª, Para, 108 pp." type="book" year="1895">Goeldi 1895</bibRefCitation>
), and we suspect that the 
<typeStatus id="131A8869FFEBFFA8FF152FCEFF11F926" box="[136,184,1755,1781]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">type</typeStatus>
species of the genus may have been collected in this region
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CC1E36CBFFEBFFA8FF202FEAFB13F823" blockId="2.[136,1452,1430,2033]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249">
